MAURICE R. VINIKOFF, Executor of the Estate of Sadie Adelman, deceased, v. HYMAN ADELMAN. 30 So. (2nd) 748

January Term, 1947

June 6, 1947 Special Division A Rehearing denied June 23, 1947 Roland W. Granat, for appellant. Price & Price, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

Affirmed on authority of Tyre v. Wright, 144 Fla. 90, 197 So. 846; In re: Monk's Estate, 155 Fla. 240, 19 So. (2nd) 796; Ullendorf v. Brown, 156 Fla. 655, 24 So. (2nd) 37, and similar cases.

BUFORD, Acting Chief Justice, CHAPMAN, and ADAMS, JJ., and WILLIAMS, Associate Justice, concur.
